Name: Pin to Quick access
Description: Pin folder to Quick access.

Name: Copy
Description: Copy the selected items to the Clipboard.

Name: Paste
Description: Paste the contents of the Clipboard to the current location.

Name: Cut
Description: Move the selected items to the Clipboard.

Name: Copy path
Description: Copy the path of the selected items to the Clipboard.

Name: Paste shortcut
Description: Paste shortcuts to the items on the Clipboard.

Name: Move to
Description: Move the selected items to the location you choose.

Name: Copy to
Description: Copy the selected items to the location you choose.

Name: Rename
Description: Rename the selected item.

Name: New folder
Description: Create a new folder.

Name: New item
Description: Create a new item in the current location.

Name: Easy access
Description: Create a way to access the selected location quickly and work with offline files.

Name: Open
Description: Open the selected file with the default program.

Name: Edit
Description: Edit the selected files.

Name: History
Description: Show history for the selected item.

Name: Select all
Description: Select all items in this view.

Name: Select none
Description: Clear all your selections.

Name: Invert selection
Description: Reverse the current selection.

Name: Delete
Description: Move the selected items to the Recycle Bin or permanently delete them.

Name: Properties
Description: Show the properties for the selected item.

Name: Share
Description: Choose an app to share the selected files.

Name: Email
Description: Send the selected items in an email (files are sent as attachments and folders as links).

Name: Zip
Description: Create a compressed (zipped) folder that contains the selected items.

Name: Burn to disc
Description: Burn the selected items to a recordable disc.

Name: Print
Description: Send the selected files to the printer.

Name: Fax
Description: Fax the selected items.

Name: Give access to
Description: Share the selected items with other people on the network.

Name: Remove access
Description: Stop sharing the selected items.

Name: Advanced security
Description: Manually set up advanced sharing settings for the selected item.

Name: Row up
Description: Scrolls the gallery up one row

Name: Row down
